AxisChangeListener, AxisConstants, ChartChangeListener, HorizontalValuePlot, VerticalValuePlot
public class OverlaidPlot
extends CombinedPlot

Extends a CombinedPlot to implement an OverlaidPlot. At this time does not add anything new to a CombinedPlot, except a easier to read name when creating an OverlaidPlot.
